ng thng xuyn. Trong trng hp bt buc phi tc dng nhit ln tc, hy to mt lp mng bo v cho tc vi sn phm chuyn dng.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/fc/1/16/1f449_1f3fb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">??</span></span>Sau khi  b tc ng ha cht, phn ui tc s tr nn kh v gin nhanh hn hn bnh thng. V l , bn hy thng xuyn ta bt phn ui tc ny i. Bn cnh , khi dm li mu tc, bn ch nn nhum cho phn chn tc mi mc. Tuyt i trnh vic tip tc ty tc cho tc  c ty trc .\r\n\r\n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f76/1/16/1f48b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">?</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f76/1/16/1f48b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">?</span></span>Hy b ti nhng b quyt ny nh v bit u c lc mnh s dng n n<span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f76/1/16/1f48b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">?</span></span><span class=\"_5mfr _47e3\"><img class=\"img\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/f76/1/16/1f48b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">?</span></span>\r\n\r\n</div>','B quyt  duy tr nhng gam mu tc thi trang','','publish','closed','closed','','bi-quyet-de-duy-tri-nhung-gam-mau-toc-thoi-trang','','','2017-12-01 05:36:47','2017-12-01 05:36:47','',0,'http://hairsalonnguyentung.com/?post_type=news&#038;p=269',0,'news','',0),(270,2,'2017-12-01 05:35:46','2017-12-01 05:35:46','','21462822_1646729522027203_806228039927579918_n','','inherit','open','closed','','21462822_1646729522027203_806228039927579918_n','','','2017-12-01 05:35:46','2017-12-01 05:35: